snippet.title: Buildest — a game about architecture | Early access trailer
snippet.description:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1565210/Buildest/ - Wishlist us on Steam!

In Buildest, you'll become an architect traveling through time to design and build some of history's most iconic structures. From ancient pyramids to modern skyscrapers, your team of hardworking builders will bring your vision to life. But be warned - as you progress through different eras, the challenges and obstacles you'll face will only become more complex. Are you up to the task? Find out in Buildest, the ultimate test of your architectural prowess!
